<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>이메일 인증</title>
</head>
<body>
<table
  width="500"
  border="0"
  cellspacing="0"
  cellpadding="0"
  style="background: white; margin: auto; padding: 64px; border-collapse: collapse"
>
  <tr>
    <td style="padding-bottom: 32px; text-align: center">
      <img
        width="131"
        height="25"
        src="data:image/png;base64,"
        alt="Formflet Logo"
      />
    </td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td
      style="
            color: #484848;
            font-size: 25px;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            font-weight: 700;
            word-wrap: break-word;
            padding-bottom: 32px;
            text-align: center;
          "
    >
      이메일 인증번호가 도착했습니다.
    </td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td
      style="
            color: #484848;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            font-weight: 400;
            line-height: 32px;
            word-wrap: break-word;
            padding-bottom: 16px;
            text-align: center;
          "
    >
      안녕하세요, 폼플렛입니다.
    </td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td
      style="
            color: #484848;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            font-weight: 400;
            line-height: 32px;
            word-wrap: break-word;
            text-align: center;
          "
    >
      요청하신 인증번호를 발송해 드립니다.<br />아래 인증번호를 직접 입력해주세요.
    </td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td style="width: 120px; background: #f5f6f6; padding: 24px; text-align: center">
          <span
            style="
              color: #8000ff;
              font-size: 25px;
              font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
              font-weight: 700;
              word-wrap: break-word;
            "
          >
            {{code}}
          </span>
    </td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td
      style="
            color: #9fa0a0;
            font-size: 13px;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            font-weight: 400;
            word-wrap: break-word;
            text-align: center;
          "
    >
      *본 메일은 발신 전용 메일로서 회신되지 않습니다.
    </td>
  </tr>
</table>
</body>
</html>